"This file can be written but not read.  The value written should be a block "
"device number as major:minor.  e.g. 8:0 This will cause that device to be "
"attached to the array, if it is available.  It will then appear at md/dev-"
"XXX (depending on the name of the device) and further configuration is then "
"possible."
