"array there will be rd0, rd1, rd2. These are symbolic links to the "
"appropriate ``dev-XXX`` entry. Thus, for example::"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../admin-guide/md.rst:610
msgid "will show ``in_sync`` on every line."
msgstr ""

